            <h1 id="training-title">RED REVEAL</h1>
            <h3 id="training-subtitle">A New Revealing Way To Play</h3>
            <p id="training-para">The scientists at NERF Research and Development have created a new, powerful tool for use in the field. The Red Reveal lens is a peripheral component that attaches to your Switch Shot EX-3 and assists in unlocking additional blasters, finding areas within levels, and identifying weaknesses in B.O.B.’s robotic army.</p>
           
            <h3 id="red-indicator">Red Reveal Indicator</h3>
            <p id="lens">Whenever you use the Red Reveal lens, a flashing icon appears above your shield bar on the left side of the screen. Here are the places where your Red Reveal is most helpful</p>
            <div id="switch-red"></div>
            <div id="red-placeholder-row">
                <ul id="red-boxes">
                    <li id="decode-messages"></li>
                    <li id="position-two-holder"></li>
                    <li id="position-three-holder"></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <h3 id="decode">Decode Secret Messages</h3>
            <p id="decode-para">These information panels contain hidden codes that are decoded by using the Red Reveal lens. Once entered into the Codebook from the main menu, these codes either unlock new blasters or grant you bonus canisters.</p>
            <h3 id="hidden-areas">Find Hidden Areas</h3>
            <p id="hidden-para">Many levels contain hidden areas. To gain entry into these zones, you must use your Red Reveal lens to discover the correct entry code. These areas often include additional canisters and Reveal Code panels, so they are definitely worth the effort</p>
            <h3 id="weak-spots">Detect Enemy Weak Spots</h3>
            <p id="weak-para">To take down certain enemies with one shot, use red reveal tech to detect the weak spot and blast away!</p>

